stories.text:
I've had major Pinboard archiving trouble over months and months in the past, with no satifying resolution. So I had let the archival membership run out.

Recently I resubscribed, but alas, archival is again not working. At 85% of my bookmarks archival seems to have stopped.

Do all of you Pinboard users on HN not have any problems with it? Am I just the outlier?

stories.text: Do you use a search engine other than Google? If yes which one and why? I would like to stop using Google because of their tracking but I am not sure of which one to use. I tried several and I can't figure out which one gives the best results average. Each of them seem to lose compared to Google :(
